tv: rug-merged  # The ADE floor class excludes a rug but includes carpets. The COCO rug-merged includes both carpets and rugs.
platform  # A pier in COCO is sometimes labeled as platform
column4: sometimes as bridge. Note the the COCO platform includes train platforms.
runways are sometimes labeled as pavement-merged and sometimes as road.

tv: grass-merged  # Visual inspection suggets there is no difference between ADE fields and ADE grass. Or at least all ADE fields are in fact grass.
sand  # The ADE land category seems to include dirt
column5: and sand. Grass and sand are already ADE categories. So strictly speaking
column6: land was an unnecessary ADE category.
